Preliminaries:\
\
\pard\tx560\tx1940\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\li1040\ql\qnatural

\f0\b0 \cf0 Please ignore this document if you are a new user installing TeXShop for the first time. If you are upgrading from a previous version, read this and the next three sections. If you are familiar with TeXShop and want to customize it, read the remaining sections.\
